  by pierre couture an engineer and physicist working at institut de recherche dhydroquébec ireq is one of these the heir to the couture wheel motor is now marketed by tm a subsidiary that has made deals with frances dassault and heuliez to develop an electric car the cleanova of which prototypes were built in  hydroquébec announced in early  at the montreal international auto show that its engine had been chosen by tata motors to equip a demonstration version of its indica model which will be road tested in norway ireqs researchers are also working on developing new battery technologies for electric cars current research is focusing on technologies to increase range improve performance in cold weather and reduce charging time pilot programs and expansion of product rangeedit tata indica ev equipped with a tm motive motor the first commercialization of the systems started in  with the interest of cleanova and peugeot citroën had presented their new diesel hybrid citroën cmétisse equipped with the tm motor at the paris auto show in  in   units were delivered to the miljø and tata motors demonstration project in norway in  tata motors expect to sell up to  of their indica vista ev in europe and to be able to face this demand tm has upgraded its production facilities in boucherville to be able to produce up to  units of their motive powertrain systems per year if needed over the years tm has diversified its product range based on the needs of two segments of the transportation industry its motive systems are compact and power dense in order to be integrated into lightduty on and offroad vehicle platforms while the sumo motors are high torque direct drive system optimized for buses and commercial vehicles the société de transport de montréal stm announced that it would replace the aging fleet of buses with a new family of buses powered by tm engine all buses that run on the network of the stm in  should run on electricity the current fleet of  buses need  million liters of diesel each year the plan would eliminate the need of diesel and eventually reduce the greenhouse gas mass production and jointventure in chinaedit china being one of the biggest market for electric buses tm announced in  the creation of a  joint venture in china in partnership with prestolite electric beijing limited pebl tm created prestolite epropulsion systems peps under this agreement peps will produce the technologies developed by tm under license and will market them to the commercial vehicle and bus industry the tm sumo systems in  tm and peps announced the beginning of high volume production in the beijing plant as well as its first large scale commercial orders from major chinese bus manufacturers such as foton motor in may  it was announced that peps had produced and sold more than  electric bus powertrains for the chinese market later that montyh the first novabus lfse buses using tm powertrains have started operating in montreal in  tm is also supplying quebecbased lion bus with drivetrain systems as well as many other truck and bus manufacturers and integrators in north america and europe referencesedit  tm electrodynamic systems history retrieved    tm electrodynamic systems history   francoeur louisgilles  moteurroue volvo dans les traces dhydro le devoir in french retrieved    lavallée pierre  april  pourraiton construire une voiture électrique au québec  sur  in french radiocanada event occurs at    francoeur louisgilles  january  volvo sur les traces dhydro le devoir in french retrieved    provost gilles gélinas pascal  march  la voiture électrique dhydro découverte in french radiocanada retrieved    radiocanada  september  voiture électrique moteur québécois fabrication étrangère  in french retrieved    hydroquébec  january  tm partners with tata motors and miljø in electric vehicle demonstration project retrieved    francoeur louisgilles  january  hydroquébec est en voiture le devoir in french retrieved    cardinal françois  november  une ba