montreal it serves all of quebec and some other provinces of canada it invests heavily in research and development hydroquébec’s information technology department operates out of the companys montreal headquarters it is a centralized system with all key decision makers located in montreal the main role of the department is internal support training infrastructure security and business operations there is a very strong emphasis on sap technology particularly for financial and hr purposes the company operates on sapbased servers and ibm san data storage equipment hydroquebec operates its own telecom network it transmits strategic data eg for the supervisory control systems and to enable verbal communications among utility personnel whether in urban centers or in remote areas some  employees can talk to each other via this network in fact the telecommunications network covers more than half of the province network signals are transmitted over more than  circuits using fiberoptic links microwave and telephone cables they use cloud and cluster technology and have virtualized using hyperv components security is a primary focus and they will continue to invest in that area sector industry energy  utilities utilities organizations state and local government employees  revenue b fye  breaking news on investment signals date type inside scoop  staffing topic staffing operating systems company hydroquébec montreal qc opportunity seeking an analyste services clients informatique banque quebec qc jm  staffing topic staffing wireless company hydroquébec montreal qc opportunity seeking a stagiaire en administration des affaires profil qc saint hubert  staffing topic staffing wireless company hydroquébec montreal qc opportunity seeking a concepteurtrice développement informatique montreal qc hl want full access to this profile and more rainkings clients have access to over  new investment signals published daily which provide insights on spending initiatives pain points management 